Class DataTextFilterUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • ui.comp3111.DataTextFilterUI

  • public class DataTextFilterUI
extends javafx.application.Application
    DataTextFilterUI is the UI for user to select text in columns to be retained, enabling user to replace/add the filtered dataTable into the database.
    Author:
    Henry Chan
